{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "城堡剧情 爱德华的性格矫正教室",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n爱德华的性格矫正教室\\n \\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "里卡多大人，\\n今天有幸请到霍普大人前来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "你好啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "请、请多多指教……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "话说，为什么找我来？\\n我没什么头绪……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "里卡多大人想要改变自我，\\n因此希望您能给他一些建议。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "建议？什么建议？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "呜、呜呜……就、就是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "正如您所见，里卡多大人，\\n连看着对方眼睛说话都做不到。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "俗话说胆小如鼠，\\n但老鼠的胆子都比他大。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哇……这人居然轻描淡写地\\n就说出了不得了的话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "里卡多大人需要的\\n是自信和自我肯定。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "所以希望连祭司工作都干不好\\n却幻想着成为骑士、\\n盲目自信的霍普大人给些建议。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "为什么要\\n突然贬低我啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "对、对不起，对不起！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不，\\n这又不是你的错……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "而且就算你让我提建议，\\n我也没什么可说的啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我只是想成为骑士，\\n才以骑士为目标。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "里卡多也只要做自己\\n想做的事不就行了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "可、可是……\\n要是因此给别人添麻烦……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "虽然我经常和父母吵起来，\\n不过还是自己的意愿最重要。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "明白了吗，里卡多大人？\\n您需要的就是这种气概。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "好。好的……我会学习的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "嗯，看来请霍普大人来还是有用的啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哎呀，夸得我都不好意思了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "那种打碎教会窗户，\\n偷马车跑出去的气概……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "胡说什么呢！？\\n你对我就是那种印象吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "啊……\\n换做是我的话敢打碎窗户吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "等等！你别当真啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "请放心，\\n您也一定能打碎的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "嗯……谢谢你……\\n我一定会努力打碎……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "诶诶诶诶诶！？\\n为什么反而有点感动了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "不过凡事都要\\n吸取之前的教训、遵规守矩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "据我查到的文献上记载，\\n铁棍最合适用来打碎窗户。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "写下这种文章的家伙\\n才应该被敲打一顿吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "不过，铁棍也不是\\n能轻易弄到手的东西。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "（太好了……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "所以我事先\\n做好了铁棍。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "你掏出了什么东西啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "搞什么！？就像是早有预谋一样\\n掏出了铁棍，也太奇怪了吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "不，我只是觉得有备无患。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不管发生什么\\n都不需要做铁棍吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "来吧，里卡多大人。\\n拿起它，尽情地砸吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "嗯！谢谢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "你们倒是听我说啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "咦，怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "要是打碎了教会窗户，\\n会给霍普添麻烦吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊！对啊！不能砸！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "奇怪了，霍普大人不是说\\n“自己的意愿最重要吗”？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可恶！\\n我怎么会说出那种话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "不行……我还是做不到。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "我觉得打碎窗户之前，\\n还有其它能改变自己的事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "所以在那之前\\n不能给霍普添麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "……\\n里卡多大人，您终于意识到了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "您真正需要的，\\n正是这种改变自我的意愿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "啊，原来如此！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110049_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "爱德华",
            "context": "在您想主动打碎窗户前，\\n铁棍就暂时由我保管吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里卡多",
            "context": "好……好的！拜托你了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "真是一段美谈……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我会这么想才怪！\\n这到底算怎么回事啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}